# linklore — environment template.
# Copy to ".env" and fill in. The file is git-ignored; nothing here is
# baked into the binary or the repo. Process env overrides .env, so a
# one-shot `LITELLM_API_KEY=… ./linklore serve` still wins.

# ---- LLM gateway (LiteLLM in front of vLLM on the DGX) ----

# Override the LiteLLM API key. Optional in our infra: when this is empty
# the config falls back to "sk-local", which is the master key the DGX
# Spark gateway is configured with (same default graphrag uses).
# Set this to your real per-account key if/when the gateway issues one.
LITELLM_API_KEY=

# Optional overrides — uncomment if your gateway moves or you want a
# different model. The defaults live in configs/config.yaml.
# LITELLM_BASE_URL=http://192.168.1.94:8000/v1
# LINKLORE_LLM_BACKEND=litellm        # litellm | ollama (fallback)
# OLLAMA_HOST=http://192.168.1.94:11434

# ---- Server ----

# LINKLORE_ADDR=127.0.0.1:8080        # bind localhost-only by default
# LINKLORE_DB_PATH=./data/linklore.db
# LINKLORE_WORKER_CONCURRENCY=4
